{"tid":652663,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"DC又贏！DC好嘢！","createTime":"2018-05-04T04:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T06:49:24.000Z","uid":159798,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bf3fc2bff834a307aef6d3119ba60c2c2df14278","tid":652663,"uid":159798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T04:34:28.000Z","msg":"想通了，DC即將要向Marvel打反擊戰， <br />\n換高層後要拼盡全力做電影，拿取人氣。<br />\n會首先經海皇Aquaman(Suckman) 進場,先拿奧斯卡。 <br />\n然後一邊拍Blackhawk一邊拍Flashpoint，以最快速度重啟。 <br />\n成功KO復仇者4後，DC才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞深度，玩藝術，黑暗，去吹奏女權)<br />\n4年重啟宇宙, 將來就可以用小丑屌打Marvel各路英雄。 <br />\n又要幫平行宇宙和綠燈俠，電視Flash聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力幫華納打倒迪士尼霸權。 <br />\n表現好的話可以打入各大影展。 <br />\n簡直是荷里活主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想打飛機了。"},{"pid":"77cc108757517aba2a79339d43958109caab8ad2","tid":652663,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T04:38:47.000Z","msg":"cyborg票房一定可以勁過黑豹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff7e9d08b9a14b271ddcef7e249cd6470cfa42b","tid":652663,"uid":159798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77cc108757517aba2a79339d43958109caab8ad2","tid":652663,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T04:38:47.000Z","msg":"cyborg票房一定可以勁過黑豹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T04:45:26.000Z","msg":"對對！<br />\n又高科技過Ironman<br />\n又黑過Chadwick Boseman<br />\n輕鬆賺10億票房！"},{"pid":"234c81def1106165480310c82f959f93a5b9beba","tid":652663,"uid":6026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T04:48:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">D</span></span>L<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">C</span></span>成為最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7591dd9394ce3899ddfe31e684bb6e02352d6c7","tid":652663,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aff7e9d08b9a14b271ddcef7e249cd